  "content": "<p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p>在朝鲜战场双方激战中就有， <a class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/aac5a23ae29ace86db0dc57046b009fb\" data-hash=\"aac5a23ae29ace86db0dc57046b009fb\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$aac5a23ae29ace86db0dc57046b009fb\">@index</a> 的回答只知其一 不知其二，我要给出的资料恰恰是：<b>中美【伪】两军激烈交战时，火线停战谈判，为庆祝板门店谈判取得进展举行联欢会，互送锦旗和礼物 ……攻心为上兵道也</b></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><p>上下图为资料</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-58051f4888f4b14c4b3ddddc82c3315f_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"579\" data-rawheight=\"791\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2f102ae8a5209a647a05bbad18e124e4_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"579\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-58051f4888f4b14c4b3ddddc82c3315f_r.jpg\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;579&#39; height=&#39;791&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"579\" data-rawheight=\"791\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2f102ae8a5209a647a05bbad18e124e4_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"579\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-58051f4888f4b14c4b3ddddc82c3315f_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-58051f4888f4b14c4b3ddddc82c3315f_hd.jpg\"/><figcaption>中美火线停战，开联欢会</figcaption></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-450d3da814ca65108dbd53e5337ee1da_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"599\" data-rawheight=\"851\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-c20dbc12245331d03b7814b59132ae08_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"599\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-450d3da814ca65108dbd53e5337ee1da_r.jpg\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;599&#39; height=&#39;851&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"599\" data-rawheight=\"851\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-c20dbc12245331d03b7814b59132ae08_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"599\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-450d3da814ca65108dbd53e5337ee1da_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-450d3da814ca65108dbd53e5337ee1da_hd.jpg\"/><figcaption>互送锦旗和礼物，加深相互了解，为了和平</figcaption></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><p>下图与李伪军火线联欢…………某些干部过于急躁易怒……</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-a0887ca3b828266b832baf7439104f8d_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"619\" data-rawheight=\"776\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-d9a5bb7fb98888ad5e5cf444fd57ce90_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"619\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a0887ca3b828266b832baf7439104f8d_r.jpg\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;619&#39; height=&#39;776&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"619\" data-rawheight=\"776\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-d9a5bb7fb98888ad5e5cf444fd57ce90_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"619\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a0887ca3b828266b832baf7439104f8d_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-a0887ca3b828266b832baf7439104f8d_hd.jpg\"/></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-424245eabf79041a21962b18ad911471_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"608\" data-rawheight=\"890\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-e3347425